":2358894,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:37:19.000Z","msg":"你個細仔個大灣數學城抱成點? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f814e9407b0887ecb2dc9c2e031f098c77b618f1","tid":2358894,"uid":361247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"反建議計劃比美國公民+綠卡持有人免費無條件申請支那香港+支那公民身份<br />\n取消所有BNO既支籍+香港永久居民身份"},{"pid":"9bb7d777b75afbe01adeb502bbf10914097b01a1","tid":2358894,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"我寧願坐監"},{"pid":"c57d50a9a18956fbcc8696fe6a358b07cc5b4ab7","tid":2358894,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"會停電,不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12870cdf81df2d1c0b8a5a205fc32e6a6e0ce5a","tid":2358894,"uid":71335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"以前就叫人上去創業 <br />\n都叫做用低價請人租地方都叫做有個好處<br />\n<br />\n屌你 而家叫人上去返工 做平價勞工 on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f60a23a52f26998e07aefed6ca021645dc16981","tid":2358894,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71dce1052c46d99250abd2accbc1b46bfc8a854c","tid":2358894,"uid":221490,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:32:21.000Z","msg":"請所有局長行會成員GA子女一齊擁抱大灣區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"市民：老年人都應擁抱大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/